## 🛠️ Operational Workflow (Cursor Implementation)

| Phase | Action | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Service Selection** | Identify the one service you do best. | Anchor the SEO strategy. |
| **Content Cluster** | Draft 3 listicles: Companies, Tools, and Selection Criteria. | Establish topical authority. |
| **Problem Mapping** | Create separate pieces for different audience use cases. | Capture specific search intent. |

